column5: A New house in a beautiful safe community. Open space high ceiling. TV, Fast internet, refrigerator and much more. Major Highways: Immediate access to 3 major high ways. Convenience to Plano, Frisco, North Dallas, Addison, The Colony... Airports: Easily access to DFW and Love Field. Restaurants & Shopping: Willow Bend Mall & Legacy shops, restaurants. My place is good for business travelers, and families (with kids).
column8: Nice new home, Queen, WiFi, TV and refrigerator
